(def FileAnalysis
  "File Analysis is an analytic process to determine a file's status. For example: virus, trojan, benign, malicious, trusted, unauthorized, sensitive, etc."
  {:d3fend/analyzes :d3fend/File,
   :d3fend/d3fend-id "D3-FA",
   :d3fend/definition
